verbose_text: However, when A2019, which lies within the alpha helix structure, was further mutated (giving the triple mutant A1927P/A2017P/A2019P), K D increased 5-fold over that for wild-type (WT) FG-Nup214 117 (K D = 222 +/- 19 nM), in agreement with predictions by our MD simulations.
